<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; max-width: 900px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
      <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #dc2626;">Warning Verify your study's status or it will be CLOSED</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #fef2f2; border: 2px solid #dc2626; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">
        Are you still accepting participants for the study below? If you do not verify, this study will be automatically closed.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: #1e40af; margin-top: 0;"><%= @study.title %></h2>
      
      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><%= @study.short_desc %></p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Please verify the status of your study by <strong><%= @auto_close_date %></strong> or your study will be automatically closed.
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="<%= verify_status_r_studies_url(token: @verify_active_token) %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 500; margin-right: 10px;">
          Confirm still active
        </a>
        <a href="<%= verify_status_r_studies_url(token: @mark_inactive_token) %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ef4444; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 500;">
          This study is no longer accepting participants.
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <p>You received this email because you're the researcher for this study on SSStutterBuddy.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
